# AKD Website - Core Development Rules

## Project Context
Danish potato starch cooperative website (akddanmark.dk). Modern, responsive site built with Astro, Vue 3, Tailwind CSS, and Sanity CMS. Serves three audiences: job seekers, prospective shareholders, and existing shareholders.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** Astro 4.x (SSG with selective SSR)
- **Interactive Components:** Vue 3 Composition API only
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS (utility-first, no custom CSS unless necessary)
- **Language:** TypeScript (strict mode)
- **CMS:** Sanity.io
- **Analytics:** PostHog

## Language & Localization
- All content in Danish (da-DK)
- Date format: DD-MM-YYYY or DD. MMM YYYY
- Number format: 1.234,56 (comma decimal separator)
- Tone: Jordnær (down-to-earth), præcis (precise), imødekommende (welcoming)

## File Naming Conventions
- Astro components: `PascalCase.astro`
- Vue components: `PascalCase.vue`
- TypeScript utilities: `camelCase.ts`
- Pages: `kebab-case.astro`
- CSS files: `kebab-case.css`

## Import Aliases
Use `@/` for all src imports:
```typescript
import Layout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { sanityClient } from '@/lib/sanity'
```

## Code Quality Standards
- **TypeScript:** Strict mode, explicit types, no `any`
- **Performance:** Lighthouse 90+ on all metrics
- **Accessibility:** WCAG 2.1 AA minimum
- **Mobile-First:** Always design for 375px first
- **Progressive Enhancement:** CSS-first, minimal JavaScript

## Before Every Commit
- [ ] TypeScript compiles with no errors
- [ ] No console errors in browser
- [ ] Tested at 375px, 768px, 1024px
- [ ] All images have alt text
- [ ] Links are keyboard accessible
- [ ] Tailwind classes only (no inline styles)
- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG AA

